Start -
1 – Take input n for array size.
2 – Again take input for pizza price(y) and size(x).
3 – Take loop and set 
	sumX = sumX + x[i];///calculate sigma(xi)
            sumX2 = sumX2 + x[i]*x[i];///calculate sigma(x^2i)
      	sumY = sumY + y[i];///calculate sigma(yi)
      	sumXY = sumXY + x[i]*y[i];///calculate sigma(xi*yi)4 – Set 
4 – Set 
	a = (n*sumXY-sumX*sumY)/(n*sumX2-sumX*sumX);///calculate Slope
            b = (sumY - a*sumX)/n;);///calculate Intercept
5 – print a,b values.
6 – print Equation of best fitting line y = ax + b.
7 – Call price function and set future pizza size and get pizza price (money=x*inch+y;).
End.
